#. type: textblock
#: ../builder/virt-builder.pod:889
msgid ""
"I<--sm-register> starts the registration process, and requires I<--sm-"
"credentials> to be specified; the format of the C<SELECTOR> of I<--sm-"
"credentials> is one of the following formats:"
