"I<--filesystems>, I<--extra>, I<--partitions>, I<--block-devices>, I<--"
"logical-volumes>, I<--volume-groups>, I<--physical-volumes>.  (More may be "
"added to this list in future)."
msgstr ""

#. type: textblock
#: ../cat/virt-filesystems.pod:121
