"Virt-dib is intended as safe replacement for C<diskimage-builder> and its "
"C<ramdisk-image-create> mode, see L</COMPARISON WITH DISKIMAGE-BUILDER> for "
"a quick comparison with usage of C<diskimage-builder>."
