#. type: verbatim
#: ../docs/guestfs-building.pod:716
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
" chmod 0666 /dev/kvm\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: textblock
#: ../docs/guestfs-building.pod:718
msgid ""
"On some systems, the chmod will not survive a reboot, and you will need to "
"make edits to the udev configuration."
