#. type: textblock
#: ../docs/guestfs-release-notes-1.36.pod:267
msgid ""
"Large generated C source files, eg. the list of commands found in F<fish/"
"cmds.c> (and many more), have been split into smaller files to speed "
"parallel compilation."
