msgstr ""

#. type: textblock
#: ../fish/guestfish-actions.pod:4242 ../lib/guestfs-actions.pod:6835
msgid ""
"In libguestfs E<ge> 1.38, this only returns C<installed>.  Use libosinfo "
"directly to detect installer CDs."
