msgstr ""

#. type: textblock
#: ../ocaml/examples/guestfs-ocaml.pod:32
msgid ""
"There are two different programming styles supported by the OCaml bindings.  "
"You can use a module style, with each C function mapped to an OCaml function:"
msgstr ""

